  targetRoles: ["CAPE SCPM", "OpenAI FDE", "OpenAI DPM (Codex)"],
  tags: ["discovery-engine", "telemetry", "demand-signals", "pipeline"],
  prompt:
    "Eighteen months into a customer's agent program: the first wave shipped (006's lighthouses), adoption is healthy, and the scenario pipeline is empty. The envisioning workshops that launched the program have gone stale — the same executives nominate the same ideas, the 43-item backlog from year one is picked over, and the program office is planning 'Workshop Series 2' to refill the funnel. Meanwhile: the deployed agents field 2,000 queries a day (including everything they fail at), support holds six months of categorized tickets (063's taxonomy, running), and 065's segmentation just mapped exactly which roles have no fit yet. The next fifty scenarios are already written down — nobody's reading them. Build the engine.",
