    bottleneck: "The agent fleet has no consumption discipline: no client-side rate limiting, no backpressure response (throttle signals were retried into — making it worse), no caching (400 briefings re-fetched the same account objects hundreds of times), and no load review before the feature shipped — agents multiply human request patterns by orders of magnitude, and the integration was designed as if the agent were one polite user instead of four hundred simultaneous ones.",
