    synthesis: "Converts the blame thread into a visibility contract — 040's identities as load attribution, 049's insight that dashboards replace walls.",
    altitude: "The CRM team hears partnership with controls; sales hears briefings back by Wednesday, spread politely across the early morning.",
    transfer: "Agent fleets are becoming every enterprise's largest API consumers — consumption contracts, backpressure citizenship, and load-reviewed ship gates are the integration discipline the next five years demand.",
